CMMC Level 2 Study Guide

A free interactive study tool for the CMMC CCP/CCA exams covering all 110 Level 2 controls.

Launch the App: https://ctatum20.github.io/cmmc-study/


FEATURES

- All 110 Controls - organized by domain with plain-English explanations
- Progress Tracking - check off controls as you study them
- 4 Quiz Modes - Multiple Choice, Flashcards, Type Match, Domain Match
- Filter & Search - by implementation type, study status, or keywords
- Works Offline - install it as an app on your phone
- 100% Free - no account, no ads, no BS


INSTALL ON YOUR PHONE

This is a Progressive Web App (PWA) - use it like a real app!

iPhone (Safari):
1. Open the link in Safari
2. Tap Share then "Add to Home Screen"

Android (Chrome):
1. Open the link in Chrome
2. Tap menu then "Install app"


IMPORTANT NOTES

- Progress saves locally on each device (browser storage)
- Progress does NOT sync between devices - your phone and laptop are separate
- Don't use Incognito/Private mode or your progress won't save
- Built from the official CMMC Level 2 Assessment Guide


STUDY TIPS

1. Work through one domain at a time
2. Check off controls as you master them
3. Use "Unstudied Only" quiz mode to target weak areas
4. Flashcard mode is great for quick review before the exam


FOR THE CPN COMMUNITY

Built for fellow CMMC professionals grinding for their certifications. Good luck on your exams!

Questions or feedback? Open an issue!


